      "inheritance_hierarchy": "ILOPool inherits: OpenZeppelin ERC721, ILOWhitelist (abstract; requires onlyProjectAdmin), ILOVest, Initializable (custom), Multicall, ILOPoolImmutableState, LiquidityManagement (which inherits PeripheryPayments + ILOPoolImmutableState and implements IUniswapV3MintCallback). ILOManager inherits OpenZeppelin Ownable and Initializable (custom). Vultisig inherits OpenZeppelin ERC20 + Ownable; VultisigWhitelisted inherits Vultisig and overrides _beforeTokenTransfer to call external Whitelist.checkWhitelist. Whitelist inherits OpenZeppelin Ownable. Libraries: TickMath/FullMath/OracleLibrary/LiquidityAmounts/PoolAddress/SqrtPriceMathPartial/TransferHelper/ChainId/PositionKey.",
      "external_dependencies": [
        "OpenZeppelin: ERC721, ERC20, Ownable, EnumerableSet, Clones",
        "Uniswap V3 Core: IUniswapV3Factory, IUniswapV3Pool, IUniswapV3MintCallback, TickMath (core variant), FixedPoint128, FullMath (core variant), FixedPoint96, SqrtPriceMath, UnsafeMath",
        "External WETH interface: IWETH9",
        "External Oracle interface: IOracle",
        "Custom interfaces: IILOManager, IILOPool, IILOWhitelist, IILOVest, IMulticall, IWhitelist, IApproveAndCallReceiver"
      ],
      "upgrade_patterns": "Factory + EIP-1167 minimal proxy clones for ILOPool instances via ILOManager.initILOPool using OpenZeppelin Clones.cloneDeterministic. No proxy-based upgradeability for deployed pools; upgrade achieved by changing ILO_POOL_IMPLEMENTATION for future clones. No Diamond pattern detected.",
      "access_control_structure": "Role model is split: (1) ILOManager Ownable owner controls global fee/config + implementation address; (2) per-project admin (cachedProject[uniV3Pool].admin) can init pools and trigger project refund claim via manager; (3) each ILOPool sets MANAGER=initializer caller (expected ILOManager) and restricts launch/claimProjectRefund to MANAGER; (4) ILOPool whitelist management restricted by onlyProjectAdmin which queries manager's cached project admin; (5) Whitelist and VultisigWhitelisted are Ownable with centralized owner authority. Note: ILOManager constructor transfers ownership to tx.origin (architectural centralization and potential mis-assignment risk)."
    },
